      about: `
      In the ever-changing landscape of disability, and with continuous changes to the NDIS, it is vital that information communicated by the AMTA is current and accurate. <br><br>
      As part of the AMTA’s Advocacy Plan, the Disability Working Group is revising and improving AMTA’s resources on music therapy in the NDIS. This is an ongoing process intended to provide AMTA members and other stakeholders with up-to-date information about music therapy and disability. <br><br>
